room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Houdini's Room Escape in Cincinnati
room_description:
It’s the height of Prohibition but folks can get a drink if they know where to look. Gangsters run underground bars where villainy flows as freely as the booze. Luckily we’ve got a man on the inside who can get you into one of these illegal speakeasies. This informant claims this bar contains enough proof of their dangerous dealings to shut them down for good.
Can you and your crew escape the Speakeasy with the evidence that will put away a dangerous gang?
